<section class="container">
  <div class="bg-white border rounded p-4">
    <h1 class="h3 mb-3">{{title}}</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">
      HET has two tutorials, one for each module. Neither requires knowledge of the other,
      so feel free to start wherever you like.
    </p>
    <div class="list-group">
      <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" href="/requests">
        <div class="fw-semibold">Requests tutorial</div>
        <div class="small text-muted">Progressive enhancement for links, forms, navigation, partial updates, request coordination, and request lifecycle hooks.</div>
      </a>
      <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" href="/components">
        <div class="fw-semibold">Components tutorial</div>
        <div class="small text-muted">Component roots, refs, signals, bindings, structural templates, lifecycle, and DOM-to-signal synchronization.</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
